uctions.</span><hr size=1> Hey Deino congrads bro.  Hey the wife put the smackdown on me after I logged (man she is still pissed).  Anyways I'll be on tomorrow for sure (thank God she works nights).  Lets start a rally to get T2 and below folks hooking up for some groups.<br><br>Again Conga rats on 46.  Planes here we come. <p>Blayne, Ranger of the 49th Winter.</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#110d03><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub59.ezboard.com/uquietas.showPublicProfile?language=EN>quietas</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://home.earthlink.net/~pdragon/pics/qbutton.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Tac-Ops Tier 1</span><br> <font color=#cc9933>(3/4/02 12:07:59 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub59.ezboard.com/fhallofheroes31576frm31.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://home.earthlink.net/~pdragon/pics/burn.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Introductions.</span><hr size=1> Quietas 60 monk<br>SS, OS, HS keys - half VP, no ST<br><br>Basically I started a monk because my old guild Back on Fennin lost its main puller a year ago. I sold off my ranger, twinked a monk, never looked back. Monks  fits like a second skin. I became main puller learning as I went since there was no other monk to learn from. I've pulled all the old zones, most of velious, very little Luclin. I was unguilded for the last 6 months so SoL raids were few and far between.<br><br>As for Alts, I have Rhyvas here who'sa  52 Ranger, geared better than I am since they actually have good buyable gear =) <p><table align=center width=500 height=125 border=0><tr><td>  <td>    <table align=left width=200 height=100 bgcolor=#C0C0C0 cellspacing=0>    <tr align=center><td colspan=2 bgcolor=0000000> <font face=Times color=crimson><b>Stormhammer</b></font> </td></tr>    <tr align=center><td nowrap style="filt