 will be posting a couple finer tuned questions for you.  Most of the time when I group with people higher than me, they say I am doing fine.<br><br>So far, I am a good puller.  Still figuring out the details with certain types of mobs... (i.e. Casters and shaman types... they just seem harder to control...)<br><br>*********************************************<br><br>Things I am currently looking for if any of you are upgrading soon or have upgraded - are boots, legs and shoulders. (I wear wu's currently...) Let me know what you have and what you are asking for it....  I am hoping to get around luclin more and find a upgrade to my fireclaw talons for a h2h weapon... (Fist of Rock from Mons Letalis is the one I have my eye on...)<br><br>RotLC quest...<br>I have all of the sashes and headbands with the exception of the last headband... I need one last peice I think.<br>Next steps are Raster and Targin the Rock.<br>Anyone who wants to help when I eventually go to do these things, I would be stoked.  I will probably do Raster myself (and I wouldn't ask anyone to help with that anyhow... Unless you all just want to whack the NPC that drops the robe for me!!   hahah...) but I need some insight on Targin.  Is that a hell camp or just the kind of thing you do with a group of 45-50ish folks?<br><br>Thats about it.<br><br>Peace - <br><br><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>   Ashremm Goldendawn </b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br><br><br><br> <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub59.ezboard.com/uashremm.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Ashremm</A> at: 3/4/02 5:42:47 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#110d03><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub59.ezboard.com/udeinonychusraptor.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Deinonychus Raptor</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#cc9933>(3/4/02 6:02:40 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub59.ezboard.com/fhallofheroes31576frm31.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?to